playstore_details.title: Bitcoin Gold Wallet by Freewallet
playstore_details.description:
Install the Bitcoin Gold Wallet and store your BTG in a secure place for free. Make easy transactions and track the price of the coin. Exchange BTG with almost any cryptocurrency directly in the app. It’s perfect for both experienced BTG miners and crypto beginners.

High-grade security
Secure your crypto with the Bitcoin Gold Wallet developed by Freewallet. Protect your money from getting into the wrong hands and lock your wallet, if you lose your phone. Restore access to your account even if you forget your private keys.

Security features include:
🔒 Fingerprint Login.
🔒 2-factor authentication.
🔒 PIN code lock.
🔒 Email confirmation for each transaction.
🔒 Daily and weekly transaction limits.

For enhanced security, most of the assets are kept in the offline cold storage. Therefore, you don't need to worry about the safety of your BTG.

Exchange functions and crypto converter
Top up your balance with almost any crypto and send coins to almost any altcoin address. All transactions between Freewallet’s users are completely free of charge. You can see your balance in fiat currencies and monitor real-time price charts. If you are keen on BTG trading, the app comes with a built-in exchange, so you can convert Bitcoin Gold to almost any other currency directly in the wallet.

Easy and comfortable to use
Enjoy the nice and user-friendly interface of Bitcoin Gold wallet by Freewallet. Log in with your email, Facebook, Google account or mobile phone number and share your wallet address on Twitter, Facebook, email, etc.

Excellent Support
The Bitcoin Gold Wallet has caring 24/7 customer support, that will assist you should problematic situations arise. The wallet is available in 13 languages including: French, German, Chinese, Spanish, and Russian.

About Freewallet
Freewallet has been a mainstay of the cryptocurrency community since 2016. It features more than 100+ cryptocurrencies including Bitcoin, Ethereum, Litecoin, Dogecoin, Monero, and Bytecoin. NewsBTC listed Freewallet as the third most popular wallet for Android in 2018.

About Bitcoin Gold
Bitcoin Gold is the result of a Bitcoin hardfork. BTG was created to provide faster mining, using GPU to greatly facilitate the mining of new blocks. As of December 2018, BTG is the 25th biggest coin based on market capitalization.

The app is available for Android 6.0 and greater
